        <font color="white" face="Verdana" size="2"> I noticed last evening that the new UI and pet control box introduces a GREAT new feature.  You can now control your pet while casting!  This is incredibly useful to a necro, for example many times I pull with darkness back to my parked pet, and as I turn around I start to cast BoD.  Well BoD is a long spell so the mob often catches up with me before I finish and am able to send in my pet to grab aggro.  No more!  Cast, pet in, finish cast, fear.  Huge upgrade to efficiency in my opinion.</P><P> </font></td>

